TITLE: Create Post with Comments (One-to-Many)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates creating a Post with multiple Comments using the `comments` attribute and `CommentFactory`. It showcases creating a single post with a fixed number of comments, creating multiple posts with a fixed number of comments each, and creating multiple posts with a range of comments.
