TITLE: Configuring Factory Namespace (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: Globally configure the default namespace for generated factories in the zenstruck_foundry configuration file. This setting specifies the root namespace under which new factory classes will be created.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: YAML
CODE:
```
# config/packages/zenstruck_foundry.yaml
zenstruck_foundry:
    make_factory:
        default_namespace: 'App\MyFactories'
```

