TITLE: Enabling Auto-Refresh on Object Proxy (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to enable auto-refreshing for an object proxy. This automatically refreshes the object from the database before calling any methods, useful in integration tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_50

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use App\Factory\PostFactory;

$post = PostFactory::new(['title' => 'Original Title'])
    ->create()
    ->_enableAutoRefresh()
;
```

