TITLE: Disabling Hints in Generated Factory (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: Configure zenstruck_foundry to remove beginner hints from generated factory files.  Setting add_hints to false in the zenstruck_foundry configuration prevents the inclusion of commented hints in the generated factory class.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: YAML
CODE:
```
# config/packages/zenstruck_foundry.yaml
zenstruck_foundry:
    make_factory:
        add_hints: false
```

