TITLE: Factory initialize() method prototype update
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates the required change in the `initialize()` method prototype in Foundry factories. In Foundry 2.0, the method must return static.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/UPGRADE-2.0.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// before
protected function initialize()
{
    // ...
}

// after
protected function initialize(): static
{
    // ...
}
```

