TITLE: Loading a Foundry Story (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to load a Zenstruck Foundry story, which executes the build() method and sets the desired state for the tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_72

LANGUAGE: php
