TITLE: Force Setting Non-Public Properties (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use helper methods to access and modify non-public properties of an object wrapped in a proxy.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_49

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// set private/protected properties
$post->_set('createdAt', new \DateTime());

// get private/protected properties
$post->_get('createdAt');
```

