TITLE: Override Initialize Method (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to override the `initialize()` method in a factory to set `withoutPersisting()` as the default behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/docs/index.rst#_snippet_39

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
protected function initialize(): static
{
    return $this
        ->withoutPersisting()
    ;
}
```

